"Sleek 87.9FM is the pulse of urban radio, delivering a dynamic mix of the hottest music, exclusive interviews, and trending topics. From breaking the latest hits in hip-hop and R&B to deep dives into indie talent, Sleek 87.9FM is your go-to for unfiltered entertainment. Tune into signature shows like 'Indie Sauce with Dream X,' 'The Afternoon Heat with Brazy Luca,' and 'Blended In The Mix with DJ Blak Friday'
for your daily dose of culture, music, and fresh perspectives."
